divs: Sighting Detailsi went outside of my house to smoke a cigarete when i saw a plane probably a dc 7 cargo plane probably heading to our airport mirabel to the the north when i saw a blinking object from the west going east. the weird thing is that the blinking was so intense that you would think the object was right above you execpt their was a slight cloud cover and the object going at incredible speed was above the clouds. what screwed me up is that you could still see the blinking light through the cloud as if the cloud wasent their. im ex-military so i know i thing or to about judging distances etc. i lost sighting to the east. being above the clouds and travelling at that speed and blinking so intensly in my mind is immpossible.
Summary: fast blinking light at high altitude
trends: There have been no other sightings in Lachine
